CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 17 reads: "Birthday Testimonial for Mrs. Robert L. Vann Is Tremendous!"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of P.L. Prattis and four women, including Jessie Vann and Mrs. Burrell K. Johnson in center, standing in interior of Penn Sheraton hotel for Jessie Vann's birthday party
